ed%20rate%20of%20%2440%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsidering%20we%20weren't%20sure%20what%20to%20expect%20and%20our%20layover%20was%20brief%2C%20we%20only%20booked%20one%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20got%20pillows%20with%20disposable%20covers%20and%20blankets.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20pillows%20with%20disposable%20covers%20on%20daybed%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6877d0f3f748d8c055f5b750%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJenny%20Powers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attendant%20gave%20us%20a%20quick%20tour%20of%20the%20communal%20restroom%2C%20which%20looked%20spotless%2C%20and%20then%20led%20us%20to%20our%20suite.%20She%20reassured%20us%20she'd%20knock%20on%20our%20door%2015%20minutes%20before%20our%20allotted%20time%20was%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20offered%20us%20pillows%20with%20disposable%20covers%20and%20a%20set%20of%20blankets%2C%20which%20we%20gratefully%20accepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20I%20would've%20preferred%20the%20pre-packaged%20airline-style%20blankets%2C%20I%20reminded%20myself%20of%20how%20many%20laundered%20hotel%20blankets%20I've%20used%20over%20my%20lifetime%20%E2%80%94%20and%20used%20it%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20the%20blankets%20felt%20clean%20and%20soft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20suite%20was%20well-appointed%20and%20laid%20out.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20Jenny%20Powers%20on%20phone%20at%20small%20desk%20in%20nap%20room%20below%20a%20smart%20TV%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6877d1eef748d8c055f5b77c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJenny%20Powers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20suite%20was%20minimally%20outfitted%20with%20a%20desk%2C%20chair%2C%20and%20a%20daybed%20with%20a%20trundle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20had%20a%20Samsung%20Smart%20TV%2C%20which%20allowed%20guests%20to%20log%20into%20their%20Netflix%20and%20Amazon%20Prime%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20was%20surprisingly%20easy%20to%20get%20some%20rest.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Minute%20Suites%20with%20desk%2C%20couch%2C%20table%2C%20lights%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6878060485e81483682e24c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20suite%20was%20big%20enough%20for%20the%20two%20of%20us%20to%20sleep%20comfortably.%3Cp%3EJenny%20Powers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20dimmed%20the%20lights%2C%20adjusted%20the%20thermostat%2C%20and%20told%20the%20in-room%20Amazon%20Alexa%20to%20play%20white%20noise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20a%20sound-masking%20system%2C%20it%20was%20remarkably%20quiet%20in%20the%20suite%20%E2%80%94%20we%20could%20still%20faintly%20hear%20attendants%20knocking%20on%20neighboring%20doors%2C%20but%20we%20eventually%20tuned%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20seems%20we%20tuned%20the%20noise%20out%20a%20little%20%3Cem%3Etoo%3C%2Fem%3E%20well%20because%20the%20next%20thing%20I%20knew%2C%20my%20phone%20alarm%20was%20going%20off.%20We'd%20both%20fallen%20into%20a%20deep%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20attendant%20said%20they'd%20knock%20on%20our%20door%2015%20minutes%20before%20our%20time%20was%20up%2C%20neither%20of%20us%20heard%20them%20do%20so.%20They%20may%20have%20forgotten%20or%20not%20knocked%20loud%20enough%20%E2%80%94%20either%20way%2C%20I%20was%20glad%20I%20set%20an%20alarm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFeeling%20surprisingly%20refreshed%2C%20we%20collected%20our%20belongings%20and%20headed%20to%20our%20gate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAll%20in%20all%2C%20our%20stay%20was%20close%20to%20perfect.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20Jenny%20powers%20and%20her%20daughter%20lying%20on%20daybed%20and%20trund