%20I%20started%20looking%20for%20new%20college%20laptops%20to%20test%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15110256068bol-20%26h%3D8f83f6aad82455e4a1b8ae68f7915fb076948f00c9b439be0e2996b2db96417e%26postID%3D688bab3cb04eda2658c40fb5%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Facer-swift-go-14-ai-laptop-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FExperiences-Qualcomm-Snapdragon-Processor-SFG14-01-X006%252Fdp%252FB0DDRKBPMY%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAcer%20Swift%20Go%2014%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20nowhere%20on%20my%20radar.%20Most%20Windows%20laptops%20use%20Intel%20or%20AMD%20processors%2C%20but%20this%20model%20uses%20a%20Qualcomm%20Snapdragon%20CPU%2C%20which%20hasn't%20traditionally%20been%20viewed%20as%20a%20top-tier%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20thank%20goodness%20I%20gave%20it%20a%20look%2C%20because%20the%20Swift%20Go%2014%20AI%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20exciting%20laptops%20I've%20reviewed.%20Its%20impressive%20performance%20has%20completely%20changed%20my%20opinion%20of%20Snapdragon%20CPUs%2C%20and%20convinced%20me%20that%20Microsoft's%20line%20of%20%26quot%3BCopilot%20Plus%26quot%3B%20PCs%20(which%20includes%20this%20laptop)%20is%20more%20than%20just%20a%20marketing%20gimmick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20all%20the%20Swift%20Go%2014%20AI%20had%20was%20a%20solid%20CPU%2C%20it%20wouldn't%20be%20worth%20the%20money.%20Luckily%2C%20Acer%20backs%20up%20the%20processor%20with%20a%20slim%20frame%2C%20a%20bright%20screen%2C%20and%20an%20absolutely%20bonkers%20amount%20of%20battery%20life.%20This%20all%20adds%20up%20to%20a%20fantastic%20productivity%20laptop%20that's%20perfect%20for%20work%20and%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227c0c3db7-ef9c-415e-93d3-687f02ac1689%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Design%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20laptop%20looks%20basic%2C%20but%20it%20feels%20great%20to%20use%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221742%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20Acer%20Swift%20Go%20AI%20laptops%20are%20angled%20in%20the%20air%20to%20show%20off%20their%20design%20in%20the%20front%20and%20back.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68950a2e194a2d49b8ae361e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221306%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlthough%20the%20Swift%20Go%2014%20AI's%20design%20is%20nothing%20to%20get%20excited%20about%2C%20we%20love%20its%20thin%2C%20lightweight%20frame.%3Cp%3EWalmart%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20age%20when%20every%20laptop%20company%20is%20trying%20to%20reinvent%20the%20MacBook%2C%20the%20Swift%20Go%2014%20AI's%20design%20isn't%20anything%20new.%20It's%20colored%20a%20dull%20silver-gray%20with%20black%20membrane%20keys%2C%20has%20visible%20hinges%2C%20and%20is%20covered%20in%20fan%20vents.%20Nothing%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20places%20that%20count%20most%2C%20the%20laptop%20shines.%20Its%20light%20weight%20%E2%80%94%20about%20three%20pounds%20%E2%80%94%20and%20slim%20frame%20make%20it%20easy%20to%20slip%20into%20a%20backpack%20or%20briefcase%2C%20or%20even%20just%20carry%20around%20under%20your%20arm.%20That%20portability%20is%20one%20of%20its%20greatest%20strengths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20helps%20that%20the%20laptop%20charges%20using%20a%20basic%20USB-C%20cable.%20This%20means%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20dealing%20with%20bulky%20AC%20adapters%20or%20charging%20bricks%20that%20weigh%20you%20down.%20A%20terabyte%20of%20included%20solid-state%20storage%20also%20means%20less%20worrying%20about%20external%20drives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20black%20membrane%20keyboard%20I%20mentioned%20might%20not%20look%20fancy%2C%20but%20it%20feels%20just%20fine.%20I've%20spent%20hours%20typing%20on%20it%2C%20and%20haven't%20felt%20any%20strain%20or%20ache.%20It%20also%20includes%20an%20adjustable%20backlight%2C%20although%20it's%20pretty%20dim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20whatever%20reason%2C%20vibrant%20displays%20are%20a%20rarity%20on%20most%20laptops%20%E2%80%94%20here%2C%20however%2C%20the%20screen%20is%20a%20highlight.%20The%2014.5-inch%20LCD%20screen%20boasts%20a%20120Hz%20refresh%20rate%20and%202560x1600%C2%A0resolution.%20Those%20are%20surprisingly%20good%20specs%20for%20a%20productivity-focused%20laptop%20like%20this%2C%20and%20give%20this%20model%20a%20little%20something%20extra%20for%20those%20who%20want%20to%20use%20it%20for%20casual%20gaming%20or%20content%20creation.%20It's%20also%20brighter%20than%20the%20industry%20average%2C%20maxing%20out%20at%20about%20400%20nits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20worth%20shouting%20out%20is%20the%20webcam.%20It's%20QHD%20(1440p)%2C%20meaning%20its%20video%20is%20four%20times%20the%20resolution%20of%20the%20industry%20standard%20720p%2C%20and%20captures%20almost%20two%20times%20the%20total%20number%20of%20pixels%20of%20a%201080p%20camera%2C%20which%20is%20often%20considered%20a%20luxury.%20It%20also%20includes%20a%20privacy%20shutter%2C%20which%20is%20always%20a%20nice%20extra.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20Swift%20Go%2014%20AI's%20design%20disappoint.%20The%20built-in%20speakers%20aren't%20awful%20%E2%80%94%20I've%20definitely%20heard%20worse%20on%20cheaper%20laptops%20%E2%80%94%20but%20they%20have%20a%20tinny%20quality%20that%20makes%20bass-heavy%20songs%20sound%20shallow.%20And%20when%20the%20laptop's%20fans%20rev%20up%20to%20full%20speed%2C%20which%20they%20often%20do%20during%20system%20updates%2C%20they%20create%20a%20surprisingly%20loud%20roar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22450dff4e-171a-47b5-b78c-044e2c0afe6c%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Performance%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPerformance%20exceeded%20my%20expectations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Acer%20Swift%20Go%2014%20AI%20laptop%20sitting%20on%20a%20table%2C%20with%20the%20desktop%20open.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6895047ccfc04e97619b0da3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Acer%20Swift%20Go%2014%20AI%20has%20a%20great%20screen%2C%20solid%20webcam%2C%20and%20long%20battery%20life.%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Antonelli%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20in%2C%20I%20expected%20the%20Acer%20Swift%20Go%2014%20AI%20to%20be%20slow%20and%20sluggish.%20Thankfully%2C%20it's%20anything%20but.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20Windows%20laptops%20use%20either%20Intel%20or%20AMD%20processors%2C%20this%20laptop%20uses%20a%20Qualcomm%20Snapdragon%20X%20Plus.%20The%20Snapdragon%20brand%20isn't%20new%2C%20but%20previous%20models%20haven't%20been%20known%20for%20their%20power.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20you'd%20usually%20find%20them%20in%20Android%20phones%20or%20tablets.%20It%20wasn't%20a%20name%20that%20inspired%20confidence%20in%20the%20laptop%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsider%20me%20surprised%20to%20find%20that%20the%20Snapdragon%20X%20Plus%20not%20only%20excels%20at%20most%20tasks%2C%20but%20also%20outperforms%20some%20pricier%20laptops.%20Geekbench%20testing%20has%20it%20coming%20in%20at%20an%20average%20CPU%20score%20of%2011%2C152%2C%20which%20is%20on%20par%20or%20better%20than%20almost%20any%20Intel%20Core%20Ultra%20chip%20and%20within%20striking%20distance%20of%20many%20top-tier%20Intel%20Core%20i9%20and%20AMD%20Ryzen%20mobile%20chips%20from%20the%20previous%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20plays%20out%20in%20practice%2C%20too.%20Programs%2C%20folders%2C%20and%20files%20run%20quickly.%20Boot%20times%20are%20also%20low.%20I%20found%20very%20few%20programs%20that%20didn't%20run%20well%20on%20it.%20Even%20the%203D-modeling%20app%20Blender%20runs%20remarkably%20smoothly%2C%20only%20lagging%20when%20it%20comes%20time%20to%20shade%20or%20render%20models.%20It%20boasts%2016GB%20of%20RAM%2C%20which%20isn't%20an%20outstanding%20achievement%20%E2%80%94%2016GB%20should%20really%20be%20the%20minimum%20in%20any%20computer%20these%20days%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20does%20help%20with%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdmittedly%2C%20the%20laptop%20does%20struggle%20in%20the%20graphics%20department.%20It's%20not%20the%20PC%20of%20choice%20for%203D%20games%20released%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20and%20video%20editing%20could%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20problem.%20And%20despite%20the%20%26quot%3BAI%26quot%3B%20branding%2C%20it's%20definitely%20not%20made%20for%20any%20sort%20of%20serious%20AI%20image-%20or%20video-generation%20work.%20Even%20integrated%20Intel%20graphics%20outpace%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20sorts%20of%20AI%20tools%2C%20like%20live%20transcription%20or%20real-time%20webcam%20enhancements%2C%20work%20much%20better%2C%20although%20I%20didn't%20find%20them%20any%20faster%20or%20otherwise%20superior%20to%20the%20AI%20tools%20on%20other%20laptops%20with%20similar%20specs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20Snapdragon%20X%20Plus%20offers%20good%20processing%20power%20but%20subpar%20graphical%20power.%20If%20that%20was%20the%20whole%20story%2C%20it%20wouldn't%20be%20that%20impressive%20%E2%80%94%20but%20to%20truly%20understand%20the%20Snapdragon%20X%20Plus'%20appeal%2C%20you%20have%20to%20look%20at%20the%20battery%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bdef61f3-83ca-4d41-bfbc-f082684dd8f5%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Battery%20life%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20has%20unbelievably%20long%20battery%20life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Acer%20Swift%20Go%2014%20AI%20laptop%20sitting%20on%20a%20table%20outside.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68950501f748d8c055f71b64%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221406%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20take%20the%20Swift%20Go%2014%20AI%20out%20all%20day%20and%20not%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20charging%20it.%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Antonelli%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20reviewing%20laptops%20for%20years%2C%20and%20I've%20come%20to%20accept%20that%20most%20great%20laptops%20also%20have%20middling-to-horrible%20battery%20life.%20Under%20usual%20load%2C%20the%20average%20Intel-%20or%20AMD-powered%20laptop%20will%20last%20about%20three%20to%20nine%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Acer%20Swift%20Go%2014%20AI%20can%20last%20between%20six%20to%2023%20hours.%20That's%20not%20an%20exaggeration.%20The%20Snapdragon%20X%20Plus%20is%20specifically%20designed%20to%20use%20less%20power%20than%20more%20standard%20chips%2C%20and%20it%20succeeds%20at%20this%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20the%20Swift%20Go%2014%20AI%20last%20for%20entire%20work%20shifts%2C%20even%20at%20max%20brightness.%20It's%20shocking%20to%20notice%20a%20low%20battery%20warning%2C%20only%20to%20check%20and%20see%20that%20your%20laptop%20still%20has%20five%20hours%20of%20life%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20this%20impressive%20battery%20performance%20that%20makes%20the%20Swift%20Go%2014%20AI%20such%20a%20great%20portable%20device.%20Even%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20charger%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20your%20laptop%20suddenly%20dying.%20It's%20a%20worthwhile%20tradeoff%20for%20the%20laptops'%20disappointing%20graphical%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dd66dc32-a995-4a16-ac0d-6def2bb7442e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Compatability%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20small%20selection%20of%20Windows%20apps%20might%20not%20run%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221532%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Acer%20Swift%20Go%2014%20AI%20laptop%20with%20Copilot%20opened.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689504b3cfc04e97619b0db2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221149%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Acer%20Swift%20Go%2014%20AI%20is%20built%20for%20productivity%20tasks.%3Cp%3EAcer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20I%20was%20impressed%20by%20its%20power%2C%20the%20laptop's%20Snapdragon%20processor%20has%20a%20specific%20li