%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20want%20to%20regret%20not%20looking%20into%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20his%20advice%20and%20ultimately%20decided%20to%20pursue%20franchising.%20I%20opened%20our%20first%20franchise%20on%20my%2030th%20birthday.%20We%20then%20opened%2054%20franchises%20in%2052%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223c1de7dd-45b3-4d04-baec-f0b9b37f24ee%5C%22%3EA%20little%20paranoia%20has%20served%20me%20well%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20my%20business%20was%20growing%2C%20more%20copycats%20were%20popping%20up.%20Entrepreneurs%20need%20a%20healthy%20level%20of%20paranoia%2C%20even%20when%20they're%20at%20the%20top.%20It%20keeps%20you%20from%20getting%20complacent.%20Just%20like%20Netflix%20replaced%20Blockbuster%20or%20the%20iPhone%20replaced%20the%20Blackberry%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20could%20be%20eclipsed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20I%20pivoted%20our%20model%20to%20an%20indoor%20adventure%20park.%20We%20removed%2080%25%20of%20the%20trampolines%20and%20reinvented%20ourselves.%20Kids%20and%20parents%20loved%20it%2C%20and%20we%20distinguished%20ourselves%20within%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20pandemic%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20portfolio%20of%20companies%20that%20enrich%20kids'%20lives.%20I%20founded%20Unleashed%20Brands%20and%20started%20acquiring%20the%20companies%20that%20impacted%20my%20own%20three%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20like%20The%20Little%20Gym.%20Today%2C%20Unleashed%20Brands%20has%20more%20than%20%241%20billion%20in%20revenue%2C%20and%20we%20serve%20more%20than%2020%20million%20kids%20around%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229c519823-466a-4a6e-93f2-62688cd219de%5C%22%3EGrit%20is%20key%20to%20being%20an%20entrepreneur%2C%20so%20I'm%20teaching%20it%20to%20my%20kids%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20my%20dad%20taught%20me%20about%20hard%20work%20and%20grit.%20I%20sometimes%20got%20up%20at%204%3A30%20a.m.%20to%20smooth%20concrete%20foundations%20with%20him.%20I%20want%20my%20three%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20who%20are%2013%2C%2010%2C%20and%205%20%E2%80%94%20to%20learn%20to%20work%20through%20challenges%20and%20not%20give%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20living%20a%20different%20lifestyle%20than%20I%20had%20growing%20up%2C%20but%20I%20find%20ways%20to%20build%20grit.%20Recently%2C%20my%20older%20daughter%20forgot%20her%20gym%20bag.%20She%20wanted%20me%20to%20deliver%20it%20to%20school%2C%20but%20I%20felt%20it%20was%20important%20that%20she%20faced%20the%20consequence%20of%20doing%20gym%20in%20her%20school%20clothes.%20She'll%20learn%20from%20that%20mistake%2C%20without%20being%20harmed%20by%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToo%20many%20people%20quit%20when%20things%20get%20hard.%20To%20be%20a%20successful%20entrepreneur%20you%20need%20to%20keep%20going%20through%20those%20difficulties%2C%20and%20give%20your%20all%20to%20your%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvestors-turned-down-trampoline-park-idea-it-makes-one-billion-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754919242000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684c3fd13d5881a51c1b6093%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvestors-turned-down-trampoline-park-idea-it-makes-one-billion-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Michael%20Browning%20Jr.%20founded%20Urban%20Air%20with%20his%20own%20savings.%20He%20was%20only%2025%20and%20investors%20and%20banks%20turned%20him%20down.%20He%20is%20teaching%20his%20kids%20grit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kelly%20Burch)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvestors-turned-down-trampoline-park-idea-it-makes-one-billion-2025-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jr%20NTR-War%202%2C%20Ashish-IGL%2C%20Aishwarya-Abhishek%3A%20Top%205%20news%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%