-mehta-bipolar-affective-disorder-bpad-recovery-journey-mental-health-awareness%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20skill%20development%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20enrolling%20them%20in%20the%20Kaushal%20Yuva%20Program%2C%20beauty%20parlours%2C%20and%20stitching%20centres%20so%20that%20they%20are%20no%20longer%20seen%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98burden%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20journey%20towards%20empowering%20young%20girls%20has%20not%20been%20easy%20for%20Roshni.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20labelled%20characterless%20because%20I%20left%20my%20abusive%20husband.%20As%20I%20was%20unable%20to%20build%20a%20family%20of%20my%20own%2C%20people%20say%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20other%20girls%20to%20settle%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20facing%20a%20set%20of%20challenges%2C%20opposition%2C%20criticism%2C%20and%20accusations%2C%20Roshni%20remains%20undeterred%20in%20her%20mission%20to%20create%20a%20child%20marriage-free%20India.%20She%20shares%20five%20key%20strategies%20to%20create%20a%20safer%20and%20more%20inclusive%20environment%20for%20young%20girls%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAdvocating%20for%20stronger%20laws%20and%20setting%20up%20a%20dedicated%20team%20to%20respond%20to%20emergencies%20in%20a%20timely%20manner.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIntegrating%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20education%20in%20school%20curricula%20so%20that%20young%20girls%20are%20aware%20of%20their%20rights.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EActivating%20existing%20child%20protection%20committees%20at%20village%2C%20block%2C%20wards%2C%20and%20district%20levels%20by%20conducting%20monthly%20review%20meetings.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEstablishing%20adolescent%20groups%20composed%20of%20champions%20from%20similar%20backgrounds%20to%20raise%20awareness%20and%20promote%20skill%20development%20among%20girls%20so%20that%20they%20can%20pursue%20a%20future%20full%20of%20opportunities.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EConducting%20