%20Park%2C%20we%20have%20about%2060%20snow%20leopards%20today.%20For%20this%20census%20camera%20traps%20were%20installed%20in%20half%20the%20total%20area%20unlike%20in%202006%20and%202012.%20If%20you%20take%20all%20of%20Ladakh%2C%20however%2C%20my%20guess%20is%20that%20the%20figure%20would%20be%20above%20250.%20This%20census%20is%20being%20carried%20out%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20the%20Wildlife%20Institute%20of%20India.%20The%20results%20of%20this%20census%20may%20come%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year%20or%20early%20next%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWildlife%20guards%20like%20Khenrab%20identify%20areas%20like%20ridgelines%2C%20broken%20cliffs%2C%20deep%20valleys%20and%20hanging%20rocks%20where%20snow%20leopards%20usually%20traverse%2C%20to%20install%20camera%20traps.%20Rolling%20and%20flat%20land%20isn%E2%80%99t%20really%20conducive%20terrain%20for%20the%20snow%20leopard%2C%20although%20for%20this%20census%20camera%20traps%20have%20been%20installed%20in%20not%20so%20conducive%20terrain%20as%20well%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20none%20are%20missed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%20wp-image-239894%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-07T124833.987-1754569909.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22From%202000%20onwards%2C%20the%20introduction%20of%20ecotourism%2C%20particularly%20in%20areas%20like%20the%20Hemis%20National%20Park%2C%20played%20a%20big%20part%20in%20preventing%20the%20snow%20leopard%20killings%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-07T124833.987-1754569909.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-07T124833.987-1754569909-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025