an%20B%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShanker%20has%20also%20been%20conferred%20with%20Progressive%20%26amp%3B%20Innovative%20Farmer%20awards%20by%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20in%202019%20and%20Innovative%20Agricultural%20Startup%20by%20the%20Startup%20India%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20images%20courtesy%20Shanker%20Meen%3C%2Fem%3Ea%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754636423000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjeevan-mushroom-3-1705068511.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D482406%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20MBA%20dropout%20in%20Jaipur%20launched%20Jeevan%20Mushroom%20in%202017%20to%20fill%20a%20gap%20in%20spawn%20availability.%20Today%20he%20runs%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20commercial%20mushroom%20spawn%20lab%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20produces%2080%20tonnes%20per%20month%2C%20supports%20export%20markets%2C%20and%20trains%20aspiring%20growers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F482406%2Fjeevan-mushroom-rajasthan-spawn-lab-startup%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20August%20is%20the%20Best%20Time%20to%20Reset%20Your%20Garden%20and%20How%20to%20Do%20It%20in%205%20Steps%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFeature%20image%20courtesy%3A%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Findian-woman-working-her-organic-vegetables-2291748213%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Shutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20garden%20looks%20worn%20out%20after%20weeks%20of%20rain%20%E2%80%94%20soggy%20soil%2C%20overgrown%20plants%2C%20and%20moss%20creeping%20into%20pots%20%E2%80%94%20you%E2%80%99re%20not%20alone.%20The%20monsoon%20brings%20life%20to%20your%20greens%2C%20but%20it%20also%20leaves%20behind%20its%20s