p%3EAnd%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20he%20does%20with%20us%2C%20too%2C%20virtually.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20history%20is%20smitten%20with%20Delhi%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDo%20you%20know%20about%20Naseem%20Mirza%20Changezi%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaseem%20came%20from%20a%20long%20line%20of%20freedom%20fighters.%20He%20was%20born%20in%201910%20in%20his%20ancestral%20home%20at%20Pahari%20Imli%20near%20the%20Churi%20Walan%20(bangle%20sellers)%20area%20of%20Old%20Delhi.%20One%20of%20Abu%E2%80%99s%20classic%20anecdotes%20to%20tell%2C%20as%20the%20group%20gathers%20around%20the%20century-old%20home%2C%20is%20of%20how%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F280138%2Fshaheed-bhagat-singh-death-anniversary-last-photograph-history-martyrs-day%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevolutionary%20Bhagat%20Singh%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20once%20sheltered%20here%20for%20a%20few%20days.%20Eventually%2C%20Singh%20was%20transferred%20to%20Daryaganj%20in%20Old%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20home%20is%20now%20inhabited%20by%20Sikander%20Mirza%20Changezi%2C%20Naseem%E2%80%99s%20son%20and%20also%20one%20of%20the%20founding%20members%20of%20the%20Hazrat%20Shah%20Waliullah%20Public%20Library.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fold-delhi-heritage-walks-1-1754405595.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Through%20Purani%20Dilli%20Walo%20Ki%20Baatein%2C%20Abu%20is%20attempting%20to%20showcase%20Delhi's%20culture%2C%20history%20and%20food%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fold-delhi-heritage-walks-1-1754405595.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fold-delhi-heritage-wa